episodes.title: Jonestown Before the Massacre | Cult Massacre: One Day in Jonestown | National Geographic
episodes.description:
Devised by Jim Jones to embody his vision of equality, Jonestown appeared to be a secluded paradise. But, beneath the facade, Jones frequently manipulated the truth to assert his authority over the increasingly vulnerable community. 

Cult Massacre: One Day in Jonestown is now streaming on Hulu.
